In addition to the global entropy calculation, the encrypted and plaintext images are divided into blocks of various sizes containing 16, 64, 256, and 1024 pixels in each block. The 3D entropy distribution plots for these blocks are displayed in Figure 5. Even with a block size of \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
