For any encryption framework, it is crucial that the secret keys used are highly sensitive. Sensitivity to secret keys means that even a tiny change in the keys makes it impossible to successfully decrypt the plaintext information. In this work, a total of fifteen secret keys (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
